This repository vendors source from Fathom, a stand-alone Syzygy tablebase
probing library, at the following paths:

    tbprobe.c
    tbprobe.h
    tbchess.c
    tbconfig.h

Upstream project: Fathom, maintained at https://github.com/jdart1/Fathom
(originally https://github.com/basil00/Fathom, no longer maintained).
License: MIT.

`stdendian.h` at the repo root is NOT vendored Fathom code -- it is a small
byte-order compatibility shim written for this project (see the file's own
header comment for details) and is covered by this project's own COPYING
(GPLv3), not by the notices below.

The copyright and permission notices below are reproduced verbatim from the
header comment of each vendored file, unmodified, as required by the MIT
license's condition that "The above copyright notice and this permission
notice shall be included in all copies or substantial portions of the
Software." Each vendored file also carries this same notice inline in its
own header -- this document collects them in one place for visibility at
the repository root.

